functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content:
I apologize for the confusion. I'll handle this request myself. Here is a list of the top 5 highest-selling video games in history and their respective genres: 

1. Tetris (Puzzle) - Often regarded as one of the most influential games of all time, Tetris' unique gameplay has earned it a special place in the industry. Its simple yet addictive nature has spanned generations and platforms, solidifying its status as one of the top-selling games. 

2. Minecraft (Sandbox) - A true phenomenon, Minecraft's open-world design and creative freedom have captivated players worldwide. Its ability to cater to various playstyles and the endless possibilities it presents have made it an enduring success. 

3. Grand Theft Auto V (Action-Adventure) - This controversial series has consistently delivered engaging stories and immersive gameplay, pushing the boundaries of what's possible in open-world action-adventure games. Its mature content and reputation for pushing the envelope have been both a blessing and a curse, but there's no denying its massive success. 

4. Wii Sports (Sports) - The Wii Sports series revolutionized the casual gaming market, offering accessible and intuitive motion-controlled sports simulations. Its appeal to a wide range of audiences, from casual players to sports enthusiasts, has made it a staple in many households. 

5. Pokémon Red and Blue (Role-Playing Game, RPG) - The Pokémon franchise has captured the imaginations of players worldwide with its unique creature-collecting and battling mechanics. This classic RPG has stood the test of time and continues to be a beloved part of gaming culture. 

Please note that sales figures can vary depending on the source and the specific version of the game, as some games have multiple editions. Additionally, the popularity and success of games can be influenced by various factors, including cultural impact and critical acclaim.
